  "title": "Cashier (Part Time/ East Area)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Are you friendly, responsible, and enjoy interacting with customers? We are looking for a Cashier to join our team!</strong></p><p><strong>📌 Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>✅ Process payments via cash, credit cards, vouchers, or debit cards.<br />✅ Issue receipts, refunds, credits, or change to customers.<br />✅ Count cash in the drawer at the start and end of shifts.<br />✅ Assist customers with inquiries and purchases.<br />✅ Answer phone calls when supervisors are unavailable.<br />✅ Take down customer requests and refer them to supervisors.<br />✅ Maintain cleanliness at the cashier counter and surrounding area.<br />✅ Pack plants or products for customers.<br />✅ Assist customers in carrying their purchases to their vehicle when necessary.</p><p><strong>📌 Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>✔️️ Comfortable working on weekends and public holidays.<br />✔️ <strong>Singaporeans or PRs only.</strong><br />✔️ Able to work on Chinese New Year’s Eve.<br />✔️ Must be able to communicate well<strong>.</strong><br />✔️ Able to work independently.</p><p>📍 <strong>Location: Bedok</strong><br />⏰ <strong>Working Hours: 9-7pm, 3-4 days per week</strong><br />💰 <strong>Salary: $12/hr</strong></p>",
